Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------TXTA-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.88,0:02:12.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經沒多少時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.05,0:02:17.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求你了  去救救天使吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.59,0:02:20.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她被天空抓住了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.04,0:02:30.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是那個怪夢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.73,0:02:34.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您醒了嗎  主人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.63,0:02:38.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nymph呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.06,0:02:39.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.28,0:02:45.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  Nymph小姐又沒回來？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.59,0:02:48.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  昨天一晚上都沒回來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.40,0:02:49.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.96,0:02:50.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.83,0:02:51.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.77,0:02:53.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一時興起不知道飛哪裡去了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.44,0:02:55.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼頭緒嗎  小智
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.11,0:02:59.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你該不會無意間傷到Nymph小姐了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.93,0:03:07.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  不  我什麼也沒做過…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.60,0:03:12.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？看樣子還是有點頭緒的嘛  櫻井君
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.65,0:03:14.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有沒有  一點也沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.06,0:03:16.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.61,0:03:20.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天傍晚  我見她飛往叢林那邊去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.64,0:03:21.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.55,0:03:24.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總感覺  她好像一副心事重重的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.97,0:03:25.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也可能是我的錯覺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.73,0:03:33.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  不一起去找找她嗎  小智
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.31,0:03:36.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天晚上要開聖誕派對的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.10,0:03:42.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正還是跟上次一樣突然回去了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.11,0:03:46.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎麼樣  邊準備邊等吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.20,0:03:50.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那先去找棵派對用的樹回來怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.32,0:03:54.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然要找  會長還是喜歡大的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.36,0:03:56.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  哪裡去找那麼大的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.95,0:03:58.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個嘛  我有點頭緒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.33,0:04:00.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家的那片河灘上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.59,0:04:02.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該有大小正合適的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.20,0:04:07.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}好棒  那樣的話就太有裝飾的價值了  小智
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.45,0:04:04.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,英君你有砍樹的工具嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.53,0:04:07.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有的話我把我珍藏的借你用用
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.19,0:04:11.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了  有劈柴用的斧子就夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.60,0:04:11.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}嗯  那麼我就先去購物了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.88,0:04:12.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後就拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.35,0:04:14.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一路走好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.13,0:04:18.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害  好快
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.45,0:04:28.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行不行  Ikaros小姐  攪得太快了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.53,0:04:29.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Stop  Stop
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.05,0:04:30.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.86,0:04:35.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  都焦掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.46,0:04:36.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.98,0:04:39.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別在意  別在意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.62,0:04:41.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  還真開心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.57,0:04:45.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能像我們這樣  兩個女生一起做蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.54,0:04:49.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是Nymph小姐也在就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.25,0:04:54.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個是？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.07,0:04:55.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.42,0:04:59.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想裝飾派對的時候可能會派上用場  就帶過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.80,0:05:02.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這麼看著  已經很開心了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.99,0:05:05.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這段時間還發生了不少事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.22,0:05:12.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這張照片  我很喜歡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.08,0:05:15.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當初見到Ikaros小姐的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.46,0:05:18.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真沒想過  我們還能玩得這麼開呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.34,0:05:20.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真高興呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.53,0:05:34.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.98,0:05:37.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正如你的情報所言  這地方真不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.51,0:05:40.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡的話  既沒地方讓那傢伙躲躲藏藏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.69,0:05:42.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,視野也相當好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.09,0:05:49.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,計劃就像剛才說的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.52,0:05:52.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利用你的反認知系統
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.05,0:05:54.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我們隱藏起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.80,0:05:56.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到危急關頭我們也會掩護你的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.27,0:05:57.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掩護？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.64,0:06:01.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超高熱體壓縮發射炮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.05,0:06:03.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「PROMETHUS」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.68,0:06:08.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把攝氏3000度氣化了的物體以每秒4千米的速度擊出
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.88,0:06:11.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要不給她展開「aegsis」的機會
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.27,0:06:14.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空之女王跟我們也沒什麼兩樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.02,0:06:16.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一瞬間就能了結她
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.11,0:06:17.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢…慢著
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.08,0:06:21.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人的命令不是破壞  而是把她帶回去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.50,0:06:24.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該在這裡說服α才對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.53,0:06:25.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.96,0:06:30.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過到了危急關頭  我們也得考慮自保才行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.49,0:06:31.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.45,0:06:34.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了避免用上這麼危險的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.10,0:06:36.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們才需要你的協助
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.84,0:06:43.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧  你一定能說服空之女王的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.31,0:06:44.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些頂多也只能算是保險措施
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.08,0:06:46.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都是主人的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.30,0:06:50.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了主人該多高興啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.93,0:06:51.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.79,0:06:54.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人會…高興
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.55,0:06:58.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.27,0:07:03.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過請答應我  在我說服她之前千萬別出手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.22,0:07:06.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是自然
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.09,0:07:21.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是知道了你的身份
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.94,0:07:24.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的「主人」會怎麼想呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.72,0:07:27.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個「大規模殺傷性武器」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.59,0:07:31.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在…幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.20,0:07:36.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nymph  這裡的天空很廣闊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.33,0:07:39.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.92,0:07:41.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們天使機器人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.66,0:07:44.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許真的從沒有會心地笑過呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.15,0:07:48.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是這樣的話  真想逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.74,0:07:53.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧？α
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.11,0:08:09.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你上哪兒去呢  Ikaros小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.09,0:08:14.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想出去…買點東西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.16,0:08:18.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼給負責買東西的小智打個電話不就…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.22,0:08:20.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.47,0:08:26.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶  Ikaros小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.41,0:08:29.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是跟我約好了  不再說謊了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.01,0:08:34.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是朋友啊  還有什麼不能說的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.94,0:08:56.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.45,0:08:59.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛋糕馬上就烤好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.48,0:09:00.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去快回哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.71,0:09:29.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.70,0:09:30.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來接我的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.54,0:09:32.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來得正好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.44,0:09:34.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就麻煩你幫拿下東西了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.94,0:09:37.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樹上的裝飾  還有響炮之類的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.53,0:09:38.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一不留神就買了很多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.72,0:09:41.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.04,0:09:42.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  對了  對了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.72,0:09:45.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看這個  很搞笑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.11,0:09:47.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪模怪樣的聖誕老人面具
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.86,0:09:51.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.02,0:09:54.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ikaros  你戴上看看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.07,0:10:00.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你戴上真太合適了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.56,0:10:05.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,道別…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.03,0:10:07.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.18,0:10:11.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是來…道別的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.76,0:10:15.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然相處的時間不長
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.57,0:10:18.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但還是承蒙您的關照了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.74,0:10:24.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我永遠不會忘記主人您的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.77,0:10:27.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.76,0:10:30.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的…從心底…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.48,0:10:33.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.19,0:10:36.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又在拿我開玩笑了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.49,0:10:38.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶  Ikaros
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.07,0:10:45.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最喜歡…你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.03,0:10:51.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的主人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.95,0:10:55.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永別了
Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------TXTB-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.20,0:11:46.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會有錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.23,0:11:49.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從天而降的攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.10,0:11:53.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轟炸掃描開始
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.75,0:11:55.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解析結果
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.95,0:11:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伏擊用天使機器人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.62,0:11:58.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Type γ  Harpy
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.02,0:12:02.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nymph的反應
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.63,0:12:08.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目標恐怕是我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.06,0:12:13.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來我將作為主人所討厭的兵器作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.15,0:12:16.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再也回不到主人身邊了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.82,0:12:18.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再也…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.45,0:12:22.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永別什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.46,0:12:25.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  好大
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.92,0:12:28.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漂亮的樹也不好找呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.73,0:12:32.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美香子無論說什麼也要棵大的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.37,0:12:33.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ikaros呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.19,0:12:33.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小智？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.66,0:12:38.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.58,0:12:40.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  小智
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.86,0:12:47.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ikaros也好  Nymph也罷
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.40,0:12:50.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不請自來  又說走就走
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.89,0:12:53.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以為我不擔心她們嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.26,0:12:55.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才討厭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.85,0:12:57.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟天使機器人一起生活什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.12,0:12:59.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要沒有了她們
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.94,0:13:03.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的生活又會恢復平靜…才對
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.43,0:13:12.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nymph
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.55,0:13:13.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真有你的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.87,0:13:16.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛一解除隱身模式就被你發現了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.87,0:13:18.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  α
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.58,0:13:22.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  有些事無論如何也想單獨跟你說
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.36,0:13:25.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然一直沒說出來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.84,0:13:26.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我真正的目的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.55,0:13:29.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是把你帶回天上去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.70,0:13:30.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.84,0:13:35.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.59,0:13:37.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來你知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.16,0:13:59.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我…在找她們啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.51,0:14:05.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你久等了  智樹
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.05,0:14:07.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,守形…學長
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.23,0:14:10.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在找Ikaros她們吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.94,0:14:15.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根據周圍目擊者提供的情報推測
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.73,0:14:17.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該沒走多遠
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.64,0:14:19.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從方向和風速
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.03,0:14:22.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及她們的身體能力考慮
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.45,0:14:24.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得在這一帶找找比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.03,0:14:25.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學長…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.07,0:14:27.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在想什麼我都一清二楚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.23,0:14:30.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上來吧  智樹
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.68,0:14:33.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太狡猾了吧  英君
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.75,0:14:37.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己一個人裝帥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.34,0:14:49.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.49,0:14:52.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和說好的不一樣嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.29,0:14:55.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說好讓我說服她的不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.54,0:14:58.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你們要突然攻擊她呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.52,0:15:01.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傻瓜  我們騙你的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.97,0:15:04.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是拜這個傻瓜所賜不是省事了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.07,0:15:07.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  謝謝了  Nymph
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.06,0:15:10.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們這麼做也是有原因的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.71,0:15:13.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人…那麼  主人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.28,0:15:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的目的是將她所持的空之女王系統的核心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.13,0:15:19.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可變式羽翼回收  僅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.92,0:15:22.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人說只用把那個拿回去就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.65,0:15:24.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說你的任務已經結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.05,0:15:26.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…你們剛剛不明明還說…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.59,0:15:29.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  快點消失  這個臭小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.94,0:15:34.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手…住手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.70,0:15:38.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼  沒想到竟這麼無趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.48,0:15:40.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜  空之女王
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.49,0:15:45.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手…智樹會傷心的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.10,0:15:51.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「paradise-song」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.10,0:15:51.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}（註：paradise-song  超超超音波震動子）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.82,0:15:55.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美香子…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.64,0:15:57.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連會長也…為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.83,0:15:59.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒時間了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.13,0:16:00.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.00,0:16:11.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小智
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.79,0:16:14.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你留在這裡等著
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.26,0:16:15.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要  我也要去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.97,0:16:17.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  在前面等著的可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.17,0:16:21.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ikaros小姐和Nymph小姐對我來說也是非常重要的朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.55,0:16:22.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要是不帶我去的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.94,0:16:26.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就用手刀打你  把你打到死
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.70,0:16:29.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.13,0:16:36.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都成粉末了  活該
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.40,0:16:40.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nymph…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.47,0:16:58.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那幅標語是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.03,0:17:00.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,見月同學的點子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.33,0:17:04.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「生日快樂  Ikaros小姐  Nymph小姐」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.20,0:17:07.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來  她們有生日嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.12,0:17:11.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒  之前問過她們但說沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.96,0:17:16.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說和學長與會長商量了一下  定了一天
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.46,0:17:19.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對天使來說  果然選擇聖誕比較好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.97,0:17:21.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要做這種事…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.43,0:17:24.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為Ikaros小姐還像是個人偶一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.18,0:17:27.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且也完全不會笑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.47,0:17:30.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nymph小姐也偶爾會露出一臉孤獨的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.89,0:17:31.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我們將今天作為
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.19,0:17:37.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「聖誕派對兼Ikaros妹妹和Nymph妹妹的生日宴會」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.95,0:17:39.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看這個  小智
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.86,0:17:43.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看  回憶相冊  楚原的收藏品哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.84,0:17:45.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真懷念呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.61,0:17:47.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是露營的時候？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.05,0:17:50.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是到海邊玩的時候吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.69,0:17:53.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看  文化祭的照片在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.31,0:17:54.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照得真不錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.26,0:18:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看了這個  Ikaros妹妹和Nymph妹妹一定會自然地笑出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.44,0:18:03.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道還能給她們做些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.54,0:18:06.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就想著從這個開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.77,0:18:08.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了智樹  一副悶悶不樂的表情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.48,0:18:13.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你其實也想過要為她們做點什麼吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.20,0:18:17.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了讓Ikaros和Nymph能打從心底裡笑出來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.28,0:18:20.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的完全不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.99,0:18:24.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光會弄哭她們  不會逗她們笑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.52,0:18:27.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要學學見月呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.24,0:18:31.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算沒什麼本事  但是總有些事情能夠做的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.53,0:18:34.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有你才能辦到的事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.75,0:18:37.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要不想後悔的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.65,0:18:48.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給她們的…生日禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.39,0:18:51.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送什麼會讓她們高興呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.88,0:18:57.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能  她可是狠狠地吃了一炮「PROMETHUS」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.97,0:19:02.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道  要麼你直接去問她們如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.55,0:19:06.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這麼做吧  但是這麼做之前首先
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.22,0:19:08.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要把她們帶回來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.33,0:19:13.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真過分…  Nymph小姐的翅膀…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.31,0:19:15.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來那麼漂亮的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.43,0:19:17.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然被扯了下來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.08,0:19:21.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可變式羽翼系統保險解除
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.56,0:19:23.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  α
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.95,0:19:25.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在智樹他們面前會露餡的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.00,0:19:29.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空之女王模式開啟
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.63,0:19:30.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,α！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.88,0:19:42.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人  對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.58,0:19:45.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至今為止我都在欺騙你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.63,0:19:50.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是戰略天使機器人  Type α  Ikaros
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.47,0:19:53.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是主人所討厭的…兵器
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.77,0:20:00.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.06,0:20:04.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶  Ikaros
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.13,0:20:07.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我之所以說討厭兵器
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.58,0:20:09.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因為覺得你太可憐了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.71,0:20:11.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.18,0:20:14.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你既疼你那顆西瓜  又在照顧小雞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.98,0:20:18.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你是個心腸很好的傢伙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.99,0:20:21.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的你  從誕生之日起便是奪人性命的工具
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.21,0:20:23.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得實在是太過分了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.12,0:20:26.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.35,0:20:29.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是呢  Ikaros
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.98,0:20:31.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在我是這麼想的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.66,0:20:34.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是一件兵器真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.59,0:20:37.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣你的朋友就能得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.86,0:20:40.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  主人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.28,0:20:44.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了  救救Nymph吧  Ikaros
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.71,0:20:46.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Type α  Ikaros
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.63,0:20:48.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.84,0:20:51.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.29,0:20:53.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡  來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.06,0:20:53.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,散開
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.99,0:20:59.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁現在  趕緊去解開Nymph的鎖鏈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.06,0:21:01.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧  Nymph
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.39,0:21:02.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真過分  背後被…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.67,0:21:05.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正她的主人也不是什麼好貨色吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.67,0:21:08.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  這麼做的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.47,0:21:19.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.47,0:21:21.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.33,0:21:33.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃我這招
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.42,0:21:39.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「aegsis」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.40,0:21:40.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係  繼續打
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.67,0:21:46.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連接
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.56,0:22:00.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.02,0:22:02.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空之女王…系統
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.79,0:22:08.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「Keres」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.29,0:22:23.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學長  怎麼做才能把這鎖鏈弄斷呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.27,0:22:24.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}不行的  而且這項圈是個炸彈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.08,0:22:28.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鎖鏈雖然耐拉  但卻不耐擰
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.88,0:22:27.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}當到爆炸時限之時會有起爆信號傳送過來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.94,0:22:31.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}隨便動它的話可能會引發誤爆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.83,0:22:31.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用斧子砍砍擰過的地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.06,0:22:32.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這麼做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.95,0:22:34.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好聽別人說話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.49,0:22:39.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連帶著你們  這一帶都會被炸飛也說不定啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.94,0:22:41.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這又如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.27,0:22:45.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是朋友啊  Nymph小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.05,0:22:47.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友有難就要幫助
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.62,0:22:50.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們只是做了些理所當然的事而已
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.54,0:22:55.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦啊  α
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.84,0:22:59.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…已經不明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.39,0:23:03.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們天使機器人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.64,0:23:08.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從誕生之日起便從沒想過什麼叫做幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.99,0:23:14.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我們是為了主人的幸福而存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.15,0:23:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是現在  我已經不明白了  自己的心思
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.27,0:23:38.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概  現在的我是幸福的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.83,0:23:45.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在的我一定能夠笑得出來
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.12,0:23:51.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶  是這樣的吧  α
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.67,0:24:12.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能從心底裡…笑出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.69,0:24:26.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確認敵對勢力已經撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.96,0:24:28.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恢復普通模式
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.42,0:24:49.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  Ikaros  怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.17,0:24:53.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.02,0:25:00.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白色聖誕
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.95,0:25:06.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真美…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.47,0:25:14.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  地上的天空…很廣闊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.78,0:27:47.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Merry  Christmas
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.13,0:27:50.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And  Happy  Birthday
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.90,0:27:51.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ikaros
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.94,0:27:52.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nymph
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.02,0:28:01.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶  Ikaros  Nymph
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.80,0:28:04.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以後就留在這裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.24,0:28:07.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.41,0:28:09.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是我送給你們的禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.95,0:28:12.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有這個是附帶的
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.92,0:28:18.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小智  不管是在什麼時候
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.38,0:28:19.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你老是這個樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.27,0:28:27.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總算笑出來了呢  α
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.53,0:28:30.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你剛才是不是笑出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.77,0:28:33.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再來  再來一次
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.82,0:28:38.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.73,0:28:41.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.59,0:28:53.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20\fad(200,200)}（生日快樂）


